Nós devolvemo-las.

764
00:48:28,375 --> 00:48:29,208
PASSAPORTE

765
00:48:29,291 --> 00:48:30,166
{\an8}A DIGITALIZAR

766
00:48:34,750 --> 00:48:35,833
