Merda!

859
00:57:16,541 --> 00:57:17,583
Merda!

860
00:57:23,041 --> 00:57:23,958
Raj!

861
00:57:34,208 --> 00:57:35,583
Meu Deus!

862
00:57:44,583 --> 00:57:45,541
Merda!

863
00:57:46,916 --> 00:57:47,875
Merda!

864
00:58:03,875 --> 00:58:06,791
<i>Lamentamos, mas a sua chamada
